snippet.title: Longplay of Rudolph The Red-Nosed Reindeer
snippet.description:
Longplay of Rudolph The Red-Nosed Reindeer, played as the NTSC version on the Wii. This game's version was released on Nov. 11th, 2010. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Main Menu
00:53 - Sorting & Decorating
03:45 - Painting Toys
06:12 - Making Cookies
08:51 - Delivering Presents
10:57 - Credits

By: PlayablePassion
